Title: Integrated generation of graphics and text: a corpus study  Topic Areas: graphics generation, corpus analysis  
Author: Marc Corio and Guy Lapalme 
Note: Submission Type: Workshop paper  Author of Record: Guy Lapalme Under consideration for other conferences (specify)? No  
Date: April 20, 1998  
